Class CurrentStates

  • java.lang.Object
    • formulation.CurrentStates
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable

    public class CurrentStates
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable

    Current State

    Class keeps the track of number of nodes currently visited, total time taken and possible next nodes It is the base of implementation of Forward Dynamic programming. Three methods for checking the precedence has been implemented, to reduce worst case complexity than that of TSP
    Version:
    20170822
    Author:
    Ritesh Agrawal
